Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的第18个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对身为重考生的我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是不是夏天都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,次等重要的还是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,成绩一直都没什么进步耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别那么沮丧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个夏天努力用功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,秋天就一定能看到成果的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真…真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为夏天是关键时刻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，本须和，加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,裕…裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这件泳装你觉得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是为了今天而买的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很…很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是个大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,清…清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,來，ちぃ衣服換好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,日比谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的到海边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明是个重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的能待在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,模拟考成绩拿 D 的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,贫穷又无暇的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，本须和，加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，周末海边见罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,海边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,新保应该已经跟你说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,三天两夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定也会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,海边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我又没那个钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,国分寺他说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,每年的这个时候\N都会到海边的别墅去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们要跟他一起同行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是免费的喔，免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,免费…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不过我们可是重考生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能去海边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ泳裝穿這件好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的旧衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,管理员小姐我也邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还有，那女孩叫裕美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都说要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，本须和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你很忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不，没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,克服夏天考验吧，重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ，去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她是电脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ，跟裕美\N還有清水老師打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是中午吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,用白天的打招呼法，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯，ちぃ真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要杵在那里多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快点换好衣服过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,游玩的时间会被耗光的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去帮帮本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,2、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,3、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有好多水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，这里就叫作“海”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要不要一起去玩水？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的海域\N深度不均匀，要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,简直像是小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这么难得的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好享受怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呸，好…好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谁叫你要东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,咸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,海水是鹹的，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,咸水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对了\N电脑碰到盐水不会有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑都有做日常防水\N所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊，说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,学长对电脑也很温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢泼我水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要一起游到那里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不勉强你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上我可不会让你溜掉的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,晚…晚上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你上特别课程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,做好觉悟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然会有间别墅在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你家果然真有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这是那个对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的私人海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只是没人来这里玩罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，检测结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会不会打扰到你们了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为大家吵吵闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是有点吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,今年的确比较热闹呢\N稔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不过偶而这样也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都到了这里，不需要看书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来玩吧！来玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好，去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要去罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要去囉，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,球，秀树给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好，开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好，开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的幸福应该就是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个不错的转换心情方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可没忘记要用功喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经打算今夏要\N从早到晚苦读了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是，是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,接着来玩扑克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得清水老师的房间应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上我会帮你上特别课程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上的课程是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一段夏季的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,门没锁，请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没人缺席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那就开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你也拿去抹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑用的防腐蚀膏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因为海风、盐水跟沙粒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,都算是精密仪器的天敌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,最好还是抹一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，不是有日常防水了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还是帮她保养一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,均匀的涂抹在全身就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,均匀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要我抹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要我幫ちぃ抹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,3、2、1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,办…办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我怎么办得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就教她自己涂抹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,听好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,先将防护膏像这样挤出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和先生\N要不要我来帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,传得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树，这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，那是貝類，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,贝类，那这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，那也是贝类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,贝类，这也是贝类吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,会走的贝类？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，这个叫什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是寄居蟹啦，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔对喔，叫寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那叫寄居蟹喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在教她词句吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ現在還有很多事不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我如果不教她的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是昆布吗？\N不，是裙带菜吗？还是海藻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,叫海草不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,海草，那是海草，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,海草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是海草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树，那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要我也来帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，拜…拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我小睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是海豚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,海…海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,海豚，是海豚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ，妳的眼力真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有海豚耶，海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它们偶而会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊，这不是很棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我只在电视上看过海豚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只在水族馆看过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，这里也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点远\N不过真的有看到对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能近一点看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道会不会游到这附近来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,说到近，如果游到这种近海来\N不就回不去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对…对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不过很少有这种机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还真想多看一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那就游到外面一点去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没多远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,学…学长，难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天你说不会游泳\N不是开玩笑的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我干嘛拿这个来开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你好歹也会蛙式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,任谁都有擅长\N与不擅长的东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊，学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是很好吗，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,联考不考游泳这科目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树不会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那样很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,明明就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,私人游艇耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对…对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,突然觉得有点火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这世界这样真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不会很不公平吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要观赏海豚\N这一带是最佳地点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚那个你有看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树看到海豚的“哗啦”\N会很高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里？在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和，还不快去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，反正她有日常防水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这么深的地方\N日常防水一点用也没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是不会游泳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,国分寺的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，学长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这么乱来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊，不经思索就跳下去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真像你的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ち…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,从表面看来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好像也没进水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树，你在生气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会生气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她真是台不可思议的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一般如果掉到海里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就会进水，然后会很难修复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不過如果ちぃ發生事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,或许会变得更麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,救本須和起來的可是ちぃ喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,2、2…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的夏天结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:21:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:21:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,次等重要的还是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这个夏天是关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,目标是成绩进步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,成绩竟然又退步了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树，夏天热吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，夏天真热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.12,0:23:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,整个人昏沉沉的，一点精神都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.75,0:23:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天要用蚊香吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,蚊香的味道\N可说是夏天的必需品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天清水老师会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:23:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天还是清水老师最棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，招待」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.64,0:24:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,乐意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,乐意之至
